The recent work of [DBLP:conf/acl/RamosRWFL24]
generates user profiles by prompting LLMs like Llama, Mistral. 
The profiles are used for rating prediction, not for ranking a larger pool of candidate items. 
The method is designed for short reviews; text-rich book reviews are not considered.